snippet.title: Card de Renketsu! Densha de GO! (trailer)
snippet.description: Card de Renketsu! Densha de GO! is a train simulator arcade game by Taito released on April 19, 2012 for the 15th anniversary of the Densha de GO! series. For the first time in the series, the player uses cards to compose his train.
